../sbin/nginx -V 查看nginx的版本以及安装的时候的参数

nginx version: nginx/1.10.3
built by gcc 5.4.0 20160609 (Ubuntu 5.4.0-6ubuntu1~16.04.4) 
built with OpenSSL 1.0.2g  1 Mar 2016
TLS SNI support enabled
configure arguments: --user=www --group=www --with-http_ssl_module --with-http_stub_status_module --prefix=/application/nginx-1.10.3


diff nginx.conf nginx.conf.default 



egrep -v "^$|#" nginx.conf.default >nginx.conf

sudo ./nginx -s reload 平滑重启


